article2.title: Hi, I'm Lucas
article2.paragraph1: I am a junior web developer, passionate about web and mobile development. I started learning web development at EFREI school in 2023. I learned to develop web and mobile applications using modern technologies and agile methods. I have acquired skills in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, Symfony, MySQL, PostgreSQL, Git, GitHub, and many others.
article2.paragraph2: I am currently looking for an internship and an apprenticeship as a junior web developer. I am open to all opportunities. I am ready to take on new challenges and learn new technologies. I am motivated, curious, autonomous, rigorous, and I enjoy working in a team. I am also passionate about music, video games, reading, traveling, and cooking.
